'''The Haven''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] established by [[Womwa]], an [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorian]], on a remote [[Planet/Legends|planet]] in the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]]. The cantina was a front, however, for Womwa's lucrative [[Spice/Legends|spice]] [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggling]] operations.<ref name="Ultimate Adversaries">''[[Ultimate Adversaries]]''</ref>

